						<summary>

						<p>Built in and incomplete. It records the grant of land to a certain Vikkiramasiṅgadēvar and his progenies with the stipulation that they have to measure out certain amount of paddy and other items to the god at Malaiyaḍikuṟichchi, other details are lost.</p>						

